Last updated: July, 2022

We do not collect any user data or make use of any third party software. 
Any data collected while using this App is stored on your device only and will be removed when you clear the App's data or remove the App from your device.

We use the services of Google Admob and Google Adsense for generating Ads. Their privacy policy can be found at: http://www.google.com/policies/privacy/

Whenever this policy changes due to an App update, this will be described in this privacy policy prior to the update.

If you have any questions or reservations regarding our privacy policy please contact us at Sudokuapps@gmail.com and we will do our best to fix the issue or help you out.
